00:01:50.730 --> 00:01:52.410
gift every year.

00:01:52.410 --> 00:01:56.480
I'd like to help join you in a
round of applause for Stuart.

00:01:56.480 --> 00:01:58.080
And we'll hear about
transformation of

00:01:58.080 --> 00:01:58.515
transportation.

